{"tid":2068869,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"少年柴灣道天橋管有一把摺刀　香淑嫻判罪名成立　還押候判","createTime":"2020-06-18T04:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T20:28:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8b609d588ff1fa5a01ab0f18e0f35ec29a7657f9","tid":2068869,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:00:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/6158\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F6158&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wUYzBSotcsoJ75UENuGtOl4%3D&h=801b6f3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/6158</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第五庭 <br />\n#香淑嫻裁判官<br />\n#1111柴灣   #裁決<br />\n<br />\n吳(18) <br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n管有違禁武器<br />\n被指於去年11月11日在柴灣道天橋上近柴灣道迴旋處，藏有違禁武器，即一把摺刀<br />\n<br />\n罪名成立，還押至6月30日等候判刑。"},{"pid":"5763c691d5c6ffc4a3a9a784b33df2cabdcd8dd4","tid":2068869,"uid":307619,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:01:01.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"200e9f42fc0cca914f30ed153bc77048ecefec87","tid":2068869,"uid":275370,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:01:09.000Z","msg":"做咩又係呢隻雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825e3e22c524577c60ffc95d244c39002e659080","tid":2068869,"uid":307619,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4F5Rdox.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4F5Rdox.jpg&h=729774aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"565d6d1fe031afd56ffff94d21d0cd4b3c307df2","tid":2068869,"uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:02:02.000Z","msg":"掌頭都可以係攻擊性武器，有手有腳入晒集中營呀笨"},{"pid":"c190154be1b519ee130406aa70a7eec108f96fc0","tid":2068869,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:02:38.000Z","msg":"藍絲界刀傷人- 坐2個月<br />\n<br />\n後生+反政府應該判2年"},{"pid":"44e69dd7658debcd0f5c0b6aaef452f6c3802499","tid":2068869,"uid":308251,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:03:57.000Z","msg":"社工呢啲左膠一早應該落地獄啦"},{"pid":"ed444f8487fd9a9655d8fbbc72de162637f20578","tid":2068869,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:04:01.000Z","msg":"又係紅官"},{"pid":"bad877e2452acc0f1c947d17dd8fb730f0311ab8","tid":2068869,"uid":338439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:04:16.000Z","msg":"多啲黎 、 密d手，又多一件"},{"pid":"031f3742d5b156d4035f9fd1f9a0c19552d92854","tid":2068869,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:05:09.000Z","msg